FBIS3-60866 "jptot001__l94114" JPRS-TOT-94-001-L Document Type:JPRS Document Title:Terrorism FOUO 7 January 1994 CENTRAL EURASIA RUSSIA Four Caucasians Kidnap Children; No Motive Given Pilots Released, Hunt for Hijackers Underway LD2612193993 Moscow Ostankino Television First Channel Network in Russian 1900 GMT 26 Dec 93 LD2612193993 Moscow Ostankino Television First Channel Network Language: Russian Article Type:BFN [From the `Novosti' newscast] [Text] Valentin Sergeyev, head of the Russian government press-service, has just told our editorial office that, following the efforts by the government headquarters and special and military sub-units, the pilots of the helicopter hijacked by the terrorists have been freed. Interior Ministry sub-units are now completing the operation to capture the terrorists.
